{"tid":121143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瓊山苑倫常命案 夫疑勒死妻後墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-02-15T04:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T04:56:20.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ec17a6cd3fad7ba251f9ef3926c12dcf06d93d","tid":121143,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3F&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=de113553\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3F&h=78f58fa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?</a><br />\n情人節翌日，鑽石山發生倫常命案。早上7時35分，有途人在瓊山苑瓊瑛閣地下，發現一名中年男子疑由高處墮下，昏迷花槽上，於是報警。救護員接報到場，將男子送到聯合醫院搶救，但告不治。警方登樓調查，在死者住所內赫然發現一名女子疑遭勒斃，初步懷疑有人殺妻後，畏罪跳樓自殺。<br />\n事後死者4女1男親屬趕往醫院了解事件，據悉，男女死者均為50多歲，兩夫婦並無子女，妻子患有腦退化，丈夫亦有皮膚病，本身是兼職的士司機，他今晨曾WhatsApp胞妹留下「生無可戀，要好好照顧家人」遺言，胞妹擔心即報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n應該唔想老婆冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </ins>"},{"pid":"41ebaaf45fe9d730bceea8a68f64b7deb1df0a6d","tid":121143,"uid":70368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"妻子患有腦退化<br />\n<br />\n因為gum似DWo"},{"pid":"a06ac15657564e197484a88773bdfe75ac0e2f69","tid":121143,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:12:30.000Z","msg":"無仔女 老婆又唔記得自己 pt揸的士搵得幾千蚊 真係生無可戀"},{"pid":"d522d1f0b05eb014a1a9b1eed138ea92a9d0fc46","tid":121143,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}